大多数[[EEPROM|EEPROM]]设备都有一定的写次数限制，某些卡已经采用了[[耗損平衡|耗損平衡]]（wear leveling）演算法，以减少经常写的位置可能出现的损耗。在記憶卡市場，售價越來越便宜，相反不同[[品牌|品牌]]的容量則競相增加。在2019年，32GB是市面常見的容量，512GB和1TB的記憶卡已經出現。

== 記憶卡類型概覽 ==
[[File:Flash_memory_cards_size.jpg|thumbnail]]
[[File:PSandPS2_MemoryCard.jpg|thumbnail]]
[[File:PC-Card_Adapter26in1.jpg|thumbnail]]]]
{{main|記憶卡之比較}}
* PCMCIA ATA Type I Flash Memory Card（PC Card ATA Type I）(max 8 GB (8 [[gibibyte|GiB]]) flash as of 2005）
** PCMCIA [[Linear_Flash|Linear Flash]] Cards, SRAM cards等。
** PCMCIA Type II, Type III cards
* CompactFlash Card (Type I), CompactFlash High-Speed（max 32 GB as of 2008）
* CompactFlash Type II, CF+(CF2.0), CF3.0
** Microdrive（max 6 GB as of 2005）
* MiniCard（[[Miniature_Card|Miniature Card]]）（max 64 MB (64 [[mebibyte|MiB]])）
* SmartMedia Card (SSFDC)（max 128 MB，3.3 V,5 V）
* xD-Picture Card, xD-Picture Card型M
* Memory Stick, MagicGate Memory Stick (max 128 MB); Memory Stick Select, MagicGate Memory Stick Select（"Select" means: 2x128 MB with A/B switch）
* SecureMMC
* Secure Digital (SD Card), Secure Digital High-Speed, Secure Digital Plus/Xtra/etc（SD with USB connector）
** miniSD Card
** microSD Card（aka Transflash, T-Flash）
** SDHC
* MU-Flash（Mu-Card，Mu-Card Alliance of OMIA）
* C-Flash
* [[SIM|SIM]]卡（Subscriber Identity Module）
* [[Smart_card|Smart card]]（ISO 7810 Card Standard , ISO 7816 Card Standard等.）
* UFC ([[USB_FlashCard|USB FlashCard]]) [https://web.archive.org/web/20060224062747/http://www.lexar.com/ufc/]（使用[[USB|USB]]）
* FISH Universal Transportable Memory Card Standard（使用USB）
* Disk memory cards:
** [[Clik!|Clik!]]（PocketZip），（40 MB PocketZip）
** [[Floppy_disk|Floppy disk]]（[[LS120|LS120]], 2-inch, 3.5-inch,等.）
* Intelligent Stick（iStick, a USB-based flash memory card with MMS）
*[[File:MicroSD與SD記憶卡.JPG|thumb]]SxS (S-by-S) memory card, a new memory card specification developed by [[Sandisk|Sandisk]] and [[Sony|Sony]]. SxS complies to the [[ExpressCard|ExpressCard]] industry standard. [http://www.dpreview.com/news/0704/07041601sxsmemorycardformat.asp] {{Wayback|url=http://www.dpreview.com/news/0704/07041601sxsmemorycardformat.asp |date=20111107015402 }}
* Nexflash [https://web.archive.org/web/20071013124716/http://winbond-usa.com/en/component/option,com_staticxt/Itemid,553/xt_item,1/staticfile,Nexflash~press_011000.htm Winbond] Serial Flash Moduel (SFM) cards, size range 1 [[millibit?|mb]], 2 mb and 4 mb.

